    <p><strong>‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßç‡¶∏:</strong> <span id="p_balance"></span> ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶æ</p>
